payment_terms.description:
Generates the HTML for the [Shop Pay Installments banner](https://shopify.dev/themes/pricing-payments/installments). The `payment_terms` filter must be used on the `form` object within a [product form](https://shopify.dev/docs/api/liquid/tags/form#form-product) or
[cart form](https://shopify.dev/docs/api/liquid/tags/form#form-cart).

```liquid
{% form 'product', product %}
  {{ form | payment_terms }}
{% endform %}
```

```liquid
{% form 'cart', cart %}
  {{ form | payment_terms }}
{% endform %}
```

---

[Shopify Liquid](https://shopify.dev/docs/api/liquid/filters/payment_terms)


